courses.learning_outcomes:
By the end of the course, students will be able to:
1. enhance competence in using English as a means of communication;
2. present ideas effectively in English in academic contexts;
3. have first-hand experience of and gain knowledge about cultures and life styles in countries where English is the mother tongue;
4. expand their repertoire of techniques in teaching English as a foreign language;
5. expand exposure to educational practices in places other than Hong Kong; and
6. provide the opportunity for participants to develop a more global outlook.

